# Keep build contexts small and reproducible.
**/node_modules
**/.venv*
**/dist
**/*.tsbuildinfo
**/.git
**/debug
**/fixtures/eval
**/fixtures/eval-real
**/scripts/eval/.cache
**/*.sf2
**/*.log
# Exclude the web app's source, but keep its package.json so pnpm can resolve the
# workspace for --frozen-lockfile (the API image never builds web).
apps/web
!apps/web/package.json
